    "title": "Configuring Group Activities"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/GroupActivities",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to bring your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "app’s users together to enjoy new and exciting shared experiences that are",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "built atop ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/shareplay",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and the FaceTime",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "infrastructure. For example, a karaoke app might offer karaoke parties where",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "several participants take part simultaneously from their own devices.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Represent shareable activities by creating objects that conform to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/GroupActivities/GroupActivity",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "protocol and, after a shared activity begins, use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/GroupActivities/GroupSession",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to synchronize that activity across participants’ devices.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-the-Group-Activities-capability-to-your-target",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add the Group Activities capability to your target",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Follow the steps in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/adding-capabilities-to-your-app#Add-a-capability",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "add the capability to your app’s target, making sure you select the Group",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Activities capability from Xcode’s Capabilities library. This capability is",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "available on all platforms except watchOS, and you must add it to an app",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "target — Group Activities aren’t available in widgets, extensions, or App",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Clips.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "group-activities",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you add the Group Activities capability, Xcode updates your target’s",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "entitlements file to include the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.group-session",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "entitlement. If Xcode automatically manages the signing of your app, it also",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "enables Group Activities for your app’s App ID.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "If you remove the Group Activities capability in Xcode, you must",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "manually update your App ID’s configuration in your developer account to disable",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "Group Activities.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you add the Group Activities capability, there are additional steps you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "must complete before your app’s users can start experiencing shared activities;",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for more information on these steps, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/GroupActivities/defining-your-apps-shareplay-activities",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/GroupActivities/joining-and-managing-a-shared-activity",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
